so many different lines of business. Whereas here, they have a lot of different lines of business,

00:17:56.900 --> 00:18:01.380
right? They have recorded music, they have merchandise, they have touring, they have publishing,

00:18:01.380 --> 00:18:05.140
they have consumer products, right, and partnerships. And so they're running a lot

00:18:05.140 --> 00:18:08.500
of different lines of business, oftentimes, the staff of between two to four people.

