00:43:59.939 --> 00:44:04.260
it works, and not just making it a black box where, hey, I ran the code and I got an output.

00:44:04.260 --> 00:44:09.219
Because, you know, it's very easy to make mistakes that way, and to use the right algorithm on the

00:44:09.219 --> 00:44:14.020
wrong problem, or use the wrong algorithm on the right problem. And, you know, those are both

00:44:14.020 --> 00:44:17.699
different types of mistakes that are easy to make in data science if you're not careful. You know,

00:44:17.699 --> 00:44:21.699
