00:45:05.780 --> 00:45:10.179
despite what some people may say. You know, like, our brains are constantly tuning and

00:45:10.179 --> 00:45:13.780
changing the different networks that we have, they're pruning connections, they're enhancing

00:45:13.780 --> 00:45:19.379
connections. And so I think the most important thing is, you know, have an open learning mindset.

00:45:20.020 --> 00:45:24.260
