00:45:44.020 --> 00:45:48.100
people learning things, especially that you're checking the assumptions. And it's like, okay,

00:45:48.100 --> 00:45:52.580
well, why did the article say to do it this way? Are there other ways we should consider doing it,

00:45:52.580 --> 00:45:59.540
